{"tid":197573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班傻鳩係咪痴撚線（2）","createTime":"2017-04-12T03:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T04:15:11.000Z","uid":63462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2737b43f5f87c2baab95373e61a5953b4779795c","tid":197573,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"冇討論價值都推爆post<br />\n連登仔ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c557ea6bbe05438c090527b692abd269db2e5a8","tid":197573,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 成班on99<br />\n<br />\n都唔知抵死個抵係邊到 個女仔就冇左條命 司機又賴左野 如果個女仔冇死你話佢抵死我可能會接受<br />\n家下人地死左 條命又補償唔到個司機d乜 仲抵人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇死 仲可以話佢抵死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時條女重傷入ICU 連登仔話佢抵死<br />\n你呢啲戇鳩偽善大愛撚咪又實係到吠<br />\n<br />\n慳啲啦 唔好再比你嘅感性蒙蔽雙眼得未啊<br />\n面對現實啦柒頭 佢鳩衝馬路 自食其果 比車車死 仲唔撚係抵死同自食惡果？<br />\n<br />\n睇你咪又係覺得佢係得15嘅女仔 死左好慘<br />\n就唔想有人批評<br />\n<br />\n完全將個人感性加諸係事實上 戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc349c65b86b25bf1f9903f5029575a092428eb","tid":197573,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7112f86c38ba0408c9f3180ecf1420de3b405511","tid":197573,"uid":80944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"講真，如果附近多死車司機就應該開慢少少"},{"pid":"8df9a987e6e4177307d790596909f240340df154","tid":197573,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:22:45.000Z","msg":"其實單野冇咩價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n變左討論應否有口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab46f0e88992